<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gem" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gem,</orth> a precious stone, a jewel: <bibl n="shak. son 21.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 21, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 208" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 208</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 7, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 5.3.196" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 3, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.4.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 4, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 78</bibl>. Metaphorically: <cit><quote>he is the brooch and g. of all the nation,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a g. of women,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 108</bibl></cit>.

